      <title>中国引导共同基金、保险公司加大股票投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/china-guides-mutual-funds-insurers-to-boost-stock-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是中国政府为支撑低迷的股市而采取的最新举措，引导地方共同基金和保险公司加大股票投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/china-guides-mutual-funds-insurers-to-boost-stock-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 01:39:56 GMT</pubDate>
