    <item>
      <title>体育平台 DAZN 获得 11 亿美元贷款用于收购 Foxtel</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/sports-platform-dazn-gets-1-1-billion-loan-for-foxtel-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国体育流媒体平台 DAZN Group Ltd. 已获得一笔 18 亿澳元（11 亿美元）的贷款，用于收购澳大利亚付费电视和流媒体公司 Foxtel Group。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/sports-platform-dazn-gets-1-1-billion-loan-for-foxtel-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 01:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁征收关税 黄金价格持稳于 10 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/gold-xauusd-holds-near-highest-since-october-on-trump-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们考虑特朗普总统最近针对中国和欧盟的关税威胁可能对全球经济产生的影响，金价维持在去年10月以来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/gold-xauusd-holds-near-highest-since-october-on-trump-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 00:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受库存增加和特朗普行动影响，油价连续第六天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份行业报告显示，美国原油库存自 11 月中旬以来首次增加，市场关注特朗普总统就全球贸易做出的进一步承诺，油价小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
