    <item>
      <title>尽管面临关税威胁，美国铝业公司仍预计 2025 年铝出货量将增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/alcoa-sees-higher-aluminum-shipments-in-2025-despite-looming-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的铝生产商美国铝业公司警告称，对从加拿大进口的铝征收 25% 的关税将对美国消费产生“抑制作用”，尽管从包装到电气需求等各个方面预计需求都会强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/alcoa-sees-higher-aluminum-shipments-in-2025-despite-looming-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 21:29:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国发行 21 年来首笔韩元债券，增强外汇储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/korea-augments-its-fx-war-chest-with-first-won-bond-in-21-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正在重新使用 21 年前使用过的一种工具来稳定其货币：发行高达 20 万亿韩元（139 亿美元）的特别债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/korea-augments-its-fx-war-chest-with-first-won-bond-in-21-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪考虑降低关税、增加进口以应对特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果特朗普总统真的采取贸易行动，印度政府将评估包括贸易协议、削减关税和从美国进口更多商品等多种选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 06:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
